@RecipeApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5011

### Hämta alla recept
GET {{RecipeApi_HostAddress}}/api/recipes
Accept: application/json

### Skapa ett nytt recept (Pannkakor)
POST {{RecipeApi_HostAddress}}/api/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pannkakor",
  "description": "Klassiska svenska pannkakor",
  "prepTimeMinutes": 10,
  "cookTimeMinutes": 20,
  "servings": 4,
  "difficulty": "Easy",
  "ingredients": [
    { "name": "Mjöl", "quantity": 3, "unit": "dl" },
    { "name": "Mjölk", "quantity": 6, "unit": "dl" },
    { "name": "Ägg", "quantity": 3, "unit": "st" },
    { "name": "Salt", "quantity": 0.5, "unit": "tsk" }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Vispa ihop mjöl, mjölk och ägg till en slät smet",
    "Låt vila 30 minuter",
    "Stek i smör i het stekpanna"
  ]
}

### Hämta ett specifikt recept (ID 1)
# Obs: Fungerar bara om ID 1 faktiskt har skapats
GET {{RecipeApi_HostAddress}}/api/recipes/1
Accept: application/json

### Sök efter recept
GET {{RecipeApi_HostAddress}}/api/recipes/search?q=pannkakor
Accept: application/json

### Ta bort ett recept (ID 1)
# Obs: Fungerar bara om ID 1 faktiskt har skapats
DELETE {{RecipeApi_HostAddress}}/api/recipes/2
